(# Odoo 19 Installation Guideline) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 1\) Overview) Tj
T*
(This guide explains a production-oriented installation of **Odoo 19** on Ubuntu Server) Tj
T*
(\(22.04/24.04\), including PostgreSQL, Python virtual environment, systemd service setup, and) Tj
T*
(Nginx reverse proxy.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(> **Audience:** Linux administrators and developers who want a maintainable Odoo deployment.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 2\) Prerequisites) Tj
T*
(- Ubuntu Server 22.04 LTS or 24.04 LTS) Tj
T*
(- A user with `sudo` privileges) Tj
T*
(- At least:) Tj
T*
(  - 2 vCPU) Tj
T*
(  - 4 GB RAM \(8 GB recommended\)) Tj
T*
(  - 20+ GB free disk) Tj
T*
(- Domain name \(optional but recommended for SSL\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 3\) Update System Packages) Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(sudo apt update && sudo apt -y upgrade) Tj
T*
(sudo reboot) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 4\) Install Required Dependencies) Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(sudo apt install -y git python3-pip python3-venv python3-dev \\) Tj
T*
(  libxml2-dev libxslt1-dev zlib1g-dev libsasl2-dev libldap2-dev \\) Tj
T*
(  libjpeg-dev libpq-dev libffi-dev libssl-dev build-essential \\) Tj
T*
(  libblas-dev libatlas-base-dev liblcms2-dev libwebp-dev \\) Tj
T*
(  node-less npm wkhtmltopdf) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(> If your distribution package for `wkhtmltopdf` is outdated or has missing patches, install) Tj
T*
(the official patched build.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 5\) Install and Configure PostgreSQL) Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(sudo apt install -y postgresql) Tj
T*
(sudo -u postgres createuser -s odoo19) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
