(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Optional: set a password for the PostgreSQL role.) Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(sudo -u postgres psql) Tj
T*
(ALTER USER odoo19 WITH PASSWORD 'strong_password_here';) Tj
T*
(\\q) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 6\) Create Odoo System User) Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(sudo useradd -m -d /opt/odoo19 -U -r -s /bin/bash odoo19) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 7\) Download Odoo 19 Source Code) Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(sudo su - odoo19) Tj
T*
(git clone https://www.github.com/odoo/odoo --depth 1 --branch 19.0 /opt/odoo19/odoo) Tj
T*
(exit) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 8\) Create Python Virtual Environment and Install Requirements) Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(sudo su - odoo19) Tj
T*
(python3 -m venv /opt/odoo19/venv) Tj
T*
(source /opt/odoo19/venv/bin/activate) Tj
T*
(pip install --upgrade pip wheel) Tj
T*
(pip install -r /opt/odoo19/odoo/requirements.txt) Tj
T*
(deactivate) Tj
T*
(exit) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 9\) Create Custom Addons and Log Directories) Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(sudo mkdir -p /opt/odoo19/custom-addons) Tj
T*
(sudo mkdir -p /var/log/odoo19) Tj
T*
(sudo chown -R odoo19:odoo19 /opt/odoo19 /var/log/odoo19) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
ET
endstream
