() Tj
T*
(## 10\) Create Odoo Configuration File) Tj
T*
(Create `/etc/odoo19.conf`:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```ini) Tj
T*
([options]) Tj
T*
(admin_passwd = change_this_master_password) Tj
T*
(db_host = False) Tj
T*
(db_port = False) Tj
T*
(db_user = odoo19) Tj
T*
(db_password = False) Tj
T*
(addons_path = /opt/odoo19/odoo/addons,/opt/odoo19/custom-addons) Tj
T*
(logfile = /var/log/odoo19/odoo.log) Tj
T*
(xmlrpc_port = 8069) Tj
T*
(proxy_mode = True) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Set secure permissions:) Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(sudo chown odoo19: /etc/odoo19.conf) Tj
T*
(sudo chmod 640 /etc/odoo19.conf) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 11\) Create systemd Service) Tj
T*
(Create `/etc/systemd/system/odoo19.service`:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```ini) Tj
T*
([Unit]) Tj
T*
(Description=Odoo19) Tj
T*
(Requires=postgresql.service) Tj
T*
(After=network.target postgresql.service) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
([Service]) Tj
T*
(Type=simple) Tj
T*
(User=odoo19) Tj
T*
(Group=odoo19) Tj
T*
(ExecStart=/opt/odoo19/venv/bin/python3 /opt/odoo19/odoo/odoo-bin -c /etc/odoo19.conf) Tj
T*
(StandardOutput=journal+console) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
([Install]) Tj
T*
(WantedBy=multi-user.target) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Enable and start the service:) Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(sudo systemctl daemon-reload) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
