T*
(## 14\) Access Odoo) Tj
T*
(- URL: `http://your-server-ip:8069` \(direct\) or `https://your-domain.com` \(via Nginx + SSL\)) Tj
T*
(- Create database from the setup page.) Tj
T*
(- Set strong admin credentials.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 15\) Basic Troubleshooting) Tj
T*
(### Check service logs) Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(sudo journalctl -u odoo19 -f) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Check Odoo log file) Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(sudo tail -f /var/log/odoo19/odoo.log) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Common issues) Tj
T*
(- **Port 8069 in use**: change `xmlrpc_port` in config.) Tj
T*
(- **Permission denied**: verify ownership of `/opt/odoo19` and `/var/log/odoo19`.) Tj
T*
(- **502 Bad Gateway**: verify Odoo service is running and Nginx proxy target is) Tj
T*
(`127.0.0.1:8069`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 16\) Post-Installation Hardening Checklist) Tj
T*
(- Change `admin_passwd` in `/etc/odoo19.conf`.) Tj
T*
(- Use a strong PostgreSQL password and restrict DB access.) Tj
T*
(- Enable firewall \(`ufw`\) and allow only required ports.) Tj
T*
(- Keep packages and Odoo code updated.) Tj
T*
(- Back up PostgreSQL databases and filestore regularly.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 17\) Maintenance Commands) Tj
T*
(Restart Odoo:) Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(sudo systemctl restart odoo19) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Update Odoo code \(manual example\):) Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(sudo su - odoo19) Tj
ET
